  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink245-kilavi">talaimakaṉ ciṟaippuṟattāṉāka veṟiyaṟivuṟīit tōḻi varaivu kaṭāyatu.    </p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> The confidante urging marriage, informing about the Veṟi, while the hero was behind the hedge.
  
          
          
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink245">
<l>poyyā marapi ṉūrmutu vēlaṉ</l>
<l>kaḻaṅkumeyp paṭuttuk kaṉṉan tūkki</l>
<l>murukeṉa moḻiyu māyiṟ</l>
<l>keḻutakai kolliva ḷaṇaṅki yōṟkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>Our ancient Vēlaṉ priest</l>
        <l>of the unlying tradition,</l>
        
        <l rend="space">having revealed the “truth”</l>
        <l>using Molucca beans</l>
        <l>and lifting the Kaṉṉam image—</l>
        
        <l rend="space">if he says “Muruku,”</l>
        
        <l>would that be fitting</l>
        <l>for the man</l>
        <l>who [actually] tormented her?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
